🔹 EPIC 1: Authentication
Smaller User Stories
US-01.1 – User Registration
As a new user, I want to register an account so that I can access the platform.
US-01.2 – User Login
As a user, I want to log in securely so that I can access my dashboard.
US-01.3 – Role-Based Login
As a system, I want to identify user roles so that users see the correct dashboard (Patient/Doctor/Admin).
US-01.4 – Password Reset
As a user, I want to reset my password so that I can recover my account.
US-01.5 – Session Management
As a system, I want to manage user sessions so that unauthorized access is prevented.
